			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Environmentally, Offshore Wind Is &#8230; Fine</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">How often can you say that about an energy generation system?</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/ashley-braun/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Ashley Braun</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						July 26, 2024 | 1,400 words, about 7 minutes
					</aside>

					
